const Months = Object.freeze({
    "1" : "Leden",
    "2" : "Únor",
    "3" : "Březen",
    "4" : "Duben",
    "5" : "Květen",
    "6" : "Červen",
    "July" : "Červenec",
    "August" : "Srpen",
    "September" : "Září",
    "October" : "Říjen",
    "November" : "Listopad",
    "December" : "Prosinec",
});

export default Months;
